=======variant mars=====
contains the code for pulling the data for particular dates

In the data_pulling.py  changing the variable days_for_data_needed to the desired date you want the data to be fetched and processed.

month variable at the start can be changed to get the data for the desired month 

changing the days_for_data_needed and the month variable may be useful for fetching the specific date's data  


+++++++++    ****run hot vanilla first**** 
and make sure both the flavour_mars_main.py an hot_vanilla are on the same folder++++++++++++


